      "content": "the steam sounds okay but i'm still really worried about the wheezing. honestly i think the antihistamine is the only thing that'll work. i have some old ventolin left from like 2 years ago though, would it be safe to use that with the extra antihistamines to make sure i don't wake up choking in the middle of the night?",
